---
title: Carb Smart Beyond Meat® Koftas with Veggie Hash and Garlic Hummus
description: Inspired by the ever-tasty and oh-so-filling mezze platter, this veggie hash hits all the right notes without the need for pitas. Spiced Beyond Meat® koftas adorn golden hash packed full of peppers, carrots and zucchini. Don't forget to top it all off with garlic hummus!

